{"id": "1242092614820560896", "channel_id": "1242092614820560896", "type": 0, "author_id": "969319742718509056", "author_name": "15828894371", "author_bot": false, "content": "新融災buff的5-3會比更新前難一些，會鎖血了。\n5-3用阿紅+羊媽帶上200%死扛能穩過。雷亞的3費牌可以不用賣，羊媽複製它可以擋住BOSS兩回合暴發。道中複製紅花2費一路殺穿，留死扛扛BOSS轉三階段的重擊。也可以用混沌或者超維24去打也很容易。\n4-3我是用24帶隊混沌，基本上也沒有壓力。也可以用紅花打，更適配本關造物。\n3-3難度比較大，我用的血肉盾擊，比較輕鬆。本關可以多帶些黑印掉落。\n2-3是最簡單的關卡，可以最後再打。多上些高費卡角色觸發時靈擺效果。\n1-1難度也有點大，BOSS在1、5、9回合會打連擊。利用這個特性，最好是上旺達降低對面力量並且能完美利用反擊，扛不住的話可以找刻印衰竭。沒有旺達可以上能保留手牌的角色比如希洛、利茲，利用保留手牌降低BOSS連擊段數。", "timestamp": "2024-05-20T12:32:36.338000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}, {"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1242092615038668872", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-19-23-31-05-711_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 180343, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1242092614820560896/1242092615038668872/Screenshot_2024-05-19-23-31-05-711_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb34e4&is=69f9e364&hm=0adde1e31bfae826d5567efb7ae6b40c0bf9d52fb6c4096c15665f7788f4ef51&"}, {"id": "1242092615298453606", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-20-13-15-30-012_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 170422, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1242092614820560896/1242092615298453606/Screenshot_2024-05-20-13-15-30-012_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb34e4&is=69f9e364&hm=6830c75c6ecc507b8688f75fb2798bd71def2e5601fb529a43090308f69eeab0&"}, {"id": "1242092615571341433", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-20-19-48-39-268_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 183835, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1242092614820560896/1242092615571341433/Screenshot_2024-05-20-19-48-39-268_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb34e4&is=69f9e364&hm=0741db88a87f0730914891addb2ef88aacf1b1c5a2456aa39c1abd281c678538&"}, {"id": "1242092615873335366", "fil